Package SyntSpec

Class FLCarps

java.lang.Object
SyntSpec.SSCarps
SyntSpec.FLCarps
public class FLCarps extends SSCarps
FLCarps is a class that extends SSCarps with the variable alleleCount, which is 0 by default. Note: This variable is currently UNUSED in the simulation, but is set to 8 in the currently unused function addFLFish.
